    <item>
      <title>美国众议院通过950亿美元援助乌克兰、以色列和台湾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/house-passes-taiwan-aid-bill-to-be-combined-with-ukraine-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院周六通过了对乌克兰 610 亿美元的新援助，结束了长达六个月的政治僵局，在此期间基辅的库存因与俄罗斯的战争而减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/house-passes-taiwan-aid-bill-to-be-combined-with-ukraine-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国众议院通过对外援助计划中的新伊朗石油制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/new-iran-oil-sanctions-passed-by-us-house-in-foreign-aid-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院通过了针对伊朗石油行业的新制裁措施，该制裁措施将成为对外援助计划的一部分，该措施有望在几天内获得参议院通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/new-iran-oil-sanctions-passed-by-us-house-in-foreign-aid-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:19:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 剥离或禁止法案预计将在几天内成为美国法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-expected-to-become-us-law-within-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院周六提出一项立法，迫使 TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动有限公司剥离其所有权股份，该法案很快就会成为法律，并将其与对乌克兰和以色列的一项重要援助计划挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/tiktok-divest-or-ban-bill-expected-to-become-us-law-within-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 17:15:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管存在全球风险，智利央行行长仍认为降息仍在轨道上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-central-bank-president-sees-rate-cuts-on-track-despite-global-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利央行行长罗莎娜·科斯塔(Rosanna Costa)表示，延长全球最大降息周期之一的计划保持不变，因为政策制定者已经将新的全球风险纳入其前景中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/chile-central-bank-president-sees-rate-cuts-on-track-despite-global-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 16:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安与哈马斯就加沙问题举行正式会晤，而阿巴斯则猛烈抨击美国否决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/erdogan-hamas-official-meet-on-gaza-while-abbas-slams-us-veto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安周六会见了哈马斯政治领导人，讨论了永久停火和加速加沙人道主义援助的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/erdogan-hamas-official-meet-on-gaza-while-abbas-slams-us-veto</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 15:38:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>脱离索马里兰地区称计划于 11 月 13 日举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/breakaway-somaliland-region-says-it-plans-nov-13-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索马里分离地区索马里兰地区选举委员会表示，该地区将于 11 月 13 日举行总统和政党选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/breakaway-somaliland-region-says-it-plans-nov-13-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 14:44:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥的辛鲍姆希望负债累累的墨西哥国家石油公司走向绿色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/claudia-sheinbaum-s-pemex-plan-focuses-on-green-energy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥主要总统候选人希望通过新的重点关注清洁能源来重振该国陷入困境的国有石油公司。但首先，克劳迪娅·谢恩鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 知道她必须解决墨西哥国家石油公司 1060 亿美元的债务问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/claudia-sheinbaum-s-pemex-plan-focuses-on-green-energy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗淡化以色列最近的袭击是“玩具”所为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/middle-east-conflict-iran-says-latest-israel-counterattack-more-like-toys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗外长在评论中将以色列在周五早些时候的袭击中使用的无人机比作“玩具”，旨在淡化袭击伊朗领土的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/middle-east-conflict-iran-says-latest-israel-counterattack-more-like-toys</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 11:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
